October 04, 2014 @ Sen Lab - U of Michigan

Overview

Baseline Stationary Covariates

  • Binary : Sex, Cohort, Ethnicity, Age, Marital, Child,
  • Categorical(>2) : InstitutionID, Specialty
  • Continuous : EFE0, Neu0
  • 84 subjects

Methylation Data

  • Number of unique Genes : 23,369
  • Number of total CpG Sites : 481,178
  • Number of selected Genes : 25
  • Number of selected CpG Sites : 828

Goal

Baseline Stationary Covariates

  • Visualization (contingency tables, distribution plots)
  • Test for independence between Baseline covariates

Methylation Data

  • Gene Selection
  • Visualization of raw data (correlation, distribution)
  • Evaluate transformation methods
